    "### 1.1 ARI（Adjusted Rand Index，调整兰德指数）\n",
    "### 比较两个聚类结果相似度的标准指标，修正了“随机一致性”的影响\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.metrics import adjusted_rand_score\n",
    "\n",
    "# y_true: 真实标签; y_pred: 聚类结果（ k-means / HDBSCAN / spectral ...）\n",
    "ari = adjusted_rand_score(y_true, y_pred)\n",
    "print(ari)\n"
   ]
